{"tid":884154,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[外匯] Order Flow/成交量價格分析例子：GBP/USD","createTime":"2018-10-31T11:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T04:54:55.000Z","uid":43407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80b09adbbd920af496f7bc0daa0bd4795e7e5969","tid":884154,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/order-flow%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E9%87%8F%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90gbpusd/2224158971199368/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2Forder-flow%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E4%25BE%258B%25E5%25AD%2590gbpusd%2F2224158971199368%2F&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=732c9fa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/order-flow%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E9%87%8F%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90gbpusd/2224158971199368/</a><br />\n<br />\n今天繼續和大家分享上星期做的一個英鎊兌美元的單子。在小時圖上可見，英鎊兌美元正穩定下滑，同時並沒有看見明顯的Signs Of Strength，亦即沒有大戶平倉的痕跡，因此我們仍可看跌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTTEWE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTTEWE8.png&h=40409512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1q75yA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1q75yA.png&h=c41b74f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上週二晚上價格重回Sell order flow zone，並且是急促的上升，在二十分鐘內急升70點子，在五分鐘圖可見，當價格進入該Order flow zone時成交量大增，但價格不升反跌，是明顯的Signs of Weakness，亦是我們準備進場的第一個訊號。隨後的半小時價格窄幅上落，並形成了Climatic Volume後的第一個支持位1.3022，當價格跌穿1.3022，就是我們的入市的時候。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1Epoko.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1Epoko.png&h=8cf668c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以看到之後的一個多星期，英鎊兌美元仍穩步地繼續走低。這是一個非常簡單的setup，先確定市場趨勢，再找出Order flow zone，耐心等待價格回調，在細的timeframe閱讀成交量確認大戶的動作。利用Order flow theory，合併成交量價格分析一起使用，成效顯而易見。之後我會繼續分享更多例子分析，各位可以多多留意。"},{"pid":"6f101fedba941bd4fb757a98378cd0aa7d825efb","tid":884154,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n但點睇咩位take profit"},{"pid":"0ad58ec7771c971a860e6264c7f3da0b84bfe9de","tid":884154,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"volume 用唔用到 weekly 同 daily 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6d7fced245fc387e6a2cb64df6406e2cf174e1","tid":884154,"uid":42870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做一單係即時既？即係define 個zone 時update 一次，入zone 時update 一次，落order 時update 一次，TP/ SL 時update 一次"},{"pid":"ff0c1bd83cfbb9b24599d2c1146c5d0a360a667e","tid":884154,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f101fedba941bd4fb757a98378cd0aa7d825efb","tid":884154,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n但點睇咩位take profit"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"睇opposite order flow，係到zone之前走，又或者一概用一個fix嘅risk reward，例如1:2咁。"},{"pid":"24a222dcf18bf5ee286a20b44dfe876528c0a2e2","tid":884154,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad58ec7771c971a860e6264c7f3da0b84bfe9de","tid":884154,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"volume 用唔用到 weekly 同 daily 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"Volume對大timeframe嘅作用會細啲，始終VSA係多用係短線上"},{"pid":"5152fb9dd95bed6c1f6b95f9020809fbd817dcab","tid":884154,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":